      "title": "Fuel quota to be reserved at selected filling stations for Police Dept.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Steps will be taken to reserve a quota of fuel at selected filling stations for the Police Department, the Ministry of Power & Energy says.",
        "Accordingly, each police station in the country will be provided with allocated volumes of fuel required for its operations."
